    "What this shows: the same logical memory can be drawn in two panels that use",
    "different numeric bases (Layout A vs Layout B). The bands still connect matching",
    "byte ranges even though the addresses on the page do not line up vertically.",
    "First link: one source section id maps to one destination section id.",
    "Second link: several adjacent source section ids in from.sections are merged",
    "into one contiguous address span on the left; that whole span maps to one",
    "destination section on the right (many ids, one combined source band).",
    "Names are neutral placeholders."
